member.name: M:ClickBot2.bho.RegisterBHO(System.Type)
member.summary: When this class is registered to COM, add a new key to the BHORegistryKey to make IE use this BHO. On 64bit machine, if the platform of this assembly and the installer is x86, 32 bit IE can use this BHO. If the platform of this assembly and the installer is x64, 64 bit IE can use this BHO.
